publisher			Blackthorn Media LLC							
publish_time	 2015年8月31日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Engage in pitched combat piloting a spectacular dragon through worlds of medieval fantasy.  Dragonflight features massive, destructible environments, fast-paced combat with up to twenty enemies swarming the skies around you, ancient castles teeming with archers, and lost wizard towers shrouded in mist. Dragonflight also features a VR mode - ride your dragon through showers of flaming arrows, or dodge trees as you fly low over a fantasy landscape, hiding from enemies arrayed against you.  Dragonflight includes unique combinations of game dynamics - acrobatic flight compliments stealthly subterfuge, as you dodge from cloud to cloud, sneaking up on fortifications too large to approach out in the open.[VR mode is available on systems running current Oculus drivers. We'll add support for major VR platforms as they emerge.]						
title	 Dragonflight			
